data.description: 2 Story updated duplex in Cambridge at Heatherstone!  Upgrades galore on a premium lot adjacent to nature preserve and pond very private end unit!   This open floor plan with dramatic two-story ceilings in family room!  Eat-in kitchen with maple cabinets, Corian countertops, custom tile backsplash, in-cabinet and under-cabinet lighting, upgraded light fixtures and cabinet hardware and oversized pantry closet. Master Bedroom with double entry, Walking-closet, Bath with double vanity, sep shower & soaking tub. 2nd Bedroom with walk-in closet also. Fully updated 2nd Bath. Loft/Study (possible 3rd Bedroom) Convenient 2nd floor laundry. Attached finished 2 car Garage. Concrete stamped patio in the back while overlooking pond and nature! Additional Features also include sound system with Bose speakers in the kitchen, loft and primary bedroom. Upgrades include solid core 6-panel doors throughout, ceramic tile in the foyer, kitchen and powder room, custom light fixtures and ceiling fans. A must see!
